SURVEY TITLE: Clinical Consult Intake Form
SURVEY DESCRIPTION: The purpose of these questions is to help the medical team identify risk factors for certain diseases based on your health history, your family health history, and your current lifestyle. Based on the information you provide here and during your Clinic visit, in addition to your genetic information, you and the clinician can work together to come up with a plan for your care. To learn more, read What to Expect at a Total Health Virtual Consultation.

Please answer the following questions about your personal and family health history to the best of your knowledge.
